This project is solely aimed for creating a chatbot application.
Which uses the Google Voice Recognition, FTTS(Text  to Speech conversion).
It's an application purely developed on the Android Studio Platform and helps you to buy products in different platforms like(Amazon,Flipkart,BigBasket).
Not only to that, this application can even be used for entertaintment purpose. 
You can browse your youtube,whatsapp and different website that you can narate.
